<br>
Arcane Feedback I<br>
Self                        Lev: 20<br>
Evoc: 5 secs                Duration: 5min<br>
Mana: 100<br>
Whenever any magical damage is dealt to user, 10% of that damage is retributed back to the caster. Normal MR is applied.<br>
<br>
Arcane Feedback II<br>
Self                        Lev: 34<br>
Evoc: 5 secs                Duration: 7min<br>
Mana: 175<br>
As per Arcane Feedback I, but damage retributed is increased to 15% &amp; MR check is at -10%.<br>
<br>
Arcane Feedback III<br>
Self                        Lev: 49<br>
Evoc: 4 secs                Duration: 10min<br>
Mana: 300<br>
As per Arcane Feedback I, but damage retributed is increased to 25% &amp; MR check is at -20%<br>
<br>
Arcane Feedback IV<br>
Self                        Lev: 56<br>
Evoc: 4 secs                Duration: 20 min<br>
Mana: 450<br>
As per Arcane Feedback I, but damage retributed is increased to 40% &amp; MR check is at -35%<br>
<br>
Arcane Barrier I<br>
Group                        Lev 44<br>
Evoc 10 secs                Duration: 10 min<br>
Mana 250<br>
This is a group version of Arcane Feedback I, with the exception of longer casting time &amp; longer duration. Increased mana because it shields the whole group &amp; with AE spells each player is gonna retribute back some damage.<br>
<br>
Arcane Barrier II<br>
Group                        Lev 53<br>
Evoc 10 sec                Duration: 15 min<br>
Mana 400<br>
This is a group version of Arcane Feedback II.<br>
<br>
Arcane Barrier III<br>
Group                        Lev 58<br>
Evoc 10 sec                Duration: 20 min<br>
Mana 600<br>
This is a group version of Arcane Feedback III.<br>
<br>
Arcane Nexus I<br>
Self                        Lev 29<br>
Evoc 6 sec                Duration: 15 min<br>
Mana 75<br>
Whenever any magical damage is inflicted on self, 10% of the damage is converted to mana absorption.<br>
<br>
Arcane Nexus II<br>
Self                        Lev 49<br>
Evoc 6 sec                Duration: 20 min<br>
Mana 150<br>
As per Arcane Nexus I, but mana conversion is 20%.<br>
<br>
Arcane Nexus III<br>
Self                        Level 54<br>
Evoc 6 sec                Duration: 20 min<br>
Mana 250<br>
As per Arcane Nexus I, but mana conversion is 35%.<br>
<br>
Arcane Nexus IV<br>
Self                        Lev 58<br>
Evoc 6 sec                Duration: 30 min<br>
Mana 400<br>
As per Arcane Nexus I, but mana conversion is 50%.<br>
<br>
Nexus Barrer I<br>
Group                        Lev 44<br>
Evoc 10 sec                Duration: 20 min<br>
Mana 200<br>
Group version of Arcane Nexus I.<br>
<br>
Nexus Barrier II<br>
Group                        Lev 54<br>
Evoc 10 sec                Duration: 30 min<br>
Mana 750<br>
Group version of Arcane Nexus II.<br>
<br>
Nexus Maelstrom<br>
Self                        Lev 60<br>
Evoc 10 sec                Duration 45 min<br>
Mana 700<br>
This is the most powerful version of the line of spells. Whenever any magical damage is inflicted on the user, 70% of the damage is retributed to the mob with -80% MR. Also 70% of the damage is converted into mana.<br>
<br>
